    public abstract class RetreatActionGeneralSuperclass
extends BaseAction
    RetreatAction_GeneralSuperclass.java --- Superclass for RetreatActions.
    Notice:
    The temporary retreat-Position has to be set by subclasses since this determines if this Action can actually be taken or not.
    Author:
    P H - 10.03.2017
